      "releaseNotes": "We've fixed some minor bugs and polished up the app for an even smoother experience – because you deserve the best!\nAnd just a reminder:\nCreate Wishlists that are easy to share and update. Birthday, Christmas, or just because – we’ve got you!\nAdd Anything You Like – Found something you love online? Add it to your wishlist in seconds.\nShare with Friends & Family – Let your loved ones know exactly what you want and avoid those awkward \"Oops, I already have this\" moments.\nMaking your dream list, saving it, and sharing it has never been this easy. Download the update and make every occasion that much more exciting!",
